## 1. Gate System (`src/gate.ts`)



**Config:** `TERRAFORM_MCP_GATE` env var — `"read"` (default), `"write"`, or `"destroy"`



Each tier includes all tools from lower tiers. **Enforcement:** Tools above the configured tier are never registered — the LLM can't see them.



```

Read tier (12 tools) — default, zero infra change:

  terraform_init, terraform_validate, terraform_plan, terraform_show,

  terraform_state_list, terraform_state_show, terraform_output,

  terraform_graph, terraform_providers, terraform_fmt,

  query_graph, get_schema



Write tier (adds 3 tools) — creates/modifies infra:

  terraform_apply, terraform_import, terraform_state_mv



Destroy tier (adds 2 tools) — permanently removes infra/state:

  terraform_destroy, terraform_state_rm

```



**Defense-in-depth:** `terraform_apply` and `terraform_destroy` still require `confirm: true` even when their tier is enabled (existing pattern from `src/index.ts:166`).



